Dataset Description¶

The dataset that will be analyzed in this report is the TMDB movie data containing information   about 10,000 movies from The Movie Database (TMDB).

Question(s) for Analysis¶

  1. What is the relationship between popularity and rating of genres?
  2. Which Genre is the highest Release profile?
  3. Movies Budget Across the years?
  4. Top Rated casts based on voting

fig,ax=plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 5))

Conclusions¶

****: Throughout this data analysis, I posed questions that the industry Actors might

find useful, and I've come to several conclusions.

In the last several Years Documentary can achieve to have higly rate with less popularity so it seems it has loyal fans but less popularity since the contents in documentaries are more serious its expected to have less popularity. when we see the popularity of Adventure movie its the most popular with average rating. so we can say based on this insight adventure genre is the most popular in TMDB Movie data set.
